Package: climate4R
Title: A Framework for Climate Data Management, Analysis, and Downscaling
Version: 2.6.2
Authors@R: person(given = "Santander Meteorology Group", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                  email = "meteo@ifca.es", comment = "Institutional author")
Description: Climate4R provides a modular framework for the management, analysis, downscaling, and visualization of climate datasets, 
             integrating multiple specialized R packages based on NetCDF data formats.
